title: Bebo Cafe
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Take-out, British, English, European, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Deli cafe and bar. Specializes in making sandwiches and salad, all day breakfast food. Willing to accommodate vegan requests, like prepare sandwich with falafel, hummus, and/or salad. Also offers the likes of jacket potatoes with beans and salad.
